---
title: Fresh Mozzarella and Farro Bowls with Marinated Chickpeas
description: We're turning nourish bowls upside down with fresh, Italian-inspired flavours. With al dente farro, blistered tomatoes and herby, balsamic chickpeas, we've got the whole food pyramid covered!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fresh-mozzarella-and-farro-bowls-edf91611.jpg
